name: Liquidswap
description: Liquidswap, the No.1 Automated Market Maker (AMM) DEX on Move, powered by Pontem Network, currently leads the Aptos blockchain with the largest market share in terms of trading volume and daily active users. Developed by the innovative Pontem team and supported by top-tier venture capitalists such as Lightspeed, Faction, and Pantera, Liquidswap utilizes the distinctive Move programming language to deliver unparalleled performance and speed in peer-to-peer digital asset trading.
